# 副簽
(pos:名詞)
<explanation>
yue:除主要簽署人以外，另外負責在文件、合約或其他法律文件上簽署，以示見證或共同承擔責任嘅人（量詞：個）
eng:co‑signatory; secondary signatory
<eg>
yue:呢份租約要有兩位副簽簽字之後才生效。 (ni1 fan6 zau1 joek3 jiu3 jau5 leung5 wai6 fu3 cin1 cin1 zi6 zi1 hau6 ci1 zo2 sang1 haau3.)
eng:The lease becomes effective only after the two co‑signatories have signed it. [end of text]


